\section{Model application}
To demonstrate the concept we run the model between 1983--2010, a period during which the Indian agricultural sector, especially across the Indo-Gangetic Plain, underwent substantial change (See \citet{} for an overview). We specifically model the growth in the number of tubewells used for irrigation. We compare the simulated tubewell expansion with district level inventory data. \\

